headline.main: TWO SUBMARINES OF FRANCE JOIN US; Reach Algiers After Escape From Toulon -- Third at Sea Following Call in Spain TWO SUBMARINES OF FRANCE JOIN US

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Nov. 30 -- Two French submarines that escaped from Toulon when the Germans entered that French Mediterranean port arrived safely at Algiers today and were welcomed by Allied officers.
